title: leyeio
author: leyeio
content: Hello BitcoinTalk forum,I've Started Preparing a Project on Community and Anonymity, I'm sure it will be a fun and interesting project. Since I am alone in the project, I want to establish a team of experienced people. I am looking for people who would like to work together on this project and who can shoulder all the problems together.You can send me a message via telegram for images, sites and more details about the project.https://t.me/leyeio

comments.body: @op I suggest you should give a brief analogy of your project I mean the concept, configuration and some graphic design that would display over here to attract people attention. Due to large number of people trying to scam people through project partnership it could be very hard of you to have some good partnership or fellow who are willing and wanting to devote their to time in a project they knew nothing about.Goodluck.
